Title: Applications of the Ashtekar gravity to four dimensional hyperk√§hler  geometry and Yang-Mills Instantons
Authors: Y. Hashimoto and Y. Yasui and S. Miyagi and T. Otsuka
Abstract: The Ashtekar-Mason-Newman equations are used to construct the hyperk\"ahler metrics on four dimensional manifolds. These equations are closely related to anti self-dual Yang-Mills equations of the infinite dimensional gauge Lie algebras of all volume preserving vector fields. Several examples of hyperk\"ahler metrics are presented through the reductions of anti self-dual connections. For any gauge group anti self-dual connections on hyperk\"ahler manifolds are constructed using the solutions of both Nahm and Laplace equations.
